body:
Rules: choose 6 smokin celebs and let us know who makes your “hot list”

I was tagged by @kleinerzombie ! these arent in order of who I find most attractive, I just listed the first six I could think of that I’d play scrabble with

1) Zendaya

ever since Shake It Up, this bih has had a special place in my heart, she has fucked me up so much since realising Im not solely attracted to males and I just fffkffSJDK LOOK AT THIS ANGEL.

2) Dylan O’Brien

I’ve realised over time that a lot of people I’ve had crushes on have looked similar, and it wasnt until I saw Dylan O’Brien that I realised that a lot of my previous crushes have looked like Dylan O’Brien…without me even knowing who he was??? Idk??

3) Jenna Coleman

I’ve never had a bigger crush on a Doctor Who actress than on Jenna, holy fuck. catch me crying over how beautiful she is every time I watch a Doctor Who episode with her in it. good god she’s stunning just LOOK at her.

4) Kellin Quinn

ok so I really thought this crush would die with my emo phase but alas (I’ve never typed “alas” before and now I feel like Dumbledore), he’s still a solid 10/10 with the voice of an angel and an unproblematic heart of gold. we stan.

5) David Tennant

I’ve had a crush on David since I was literally five years old and if you think that’s ever going to change you can drown in a pot of honey.

6) Ruby Rose

watched the first three seasons of oitnb just so I knew what was going on when she arrived, and I stopped watching the moment she left. I had multiple crushes on females before realising I wasnt straight, but Ruby was the first person that made me think “fuck…have I actually been attracted to a guy? ever? I cant even remember what a guy looks like” whenever I look at her.

I tag: @babyblue65 @spookygaybe @gwenisonline

summary:
Entp's third function is Fe. This means a couple of things for them:
They are stirrers who like to get a reaction
They are...
body:
Entp week! Day four.

Entp’s third function is Fe. This means a couple of things for them:

  1. They are stirrers who like to get a reaction
  2. They are secretly sensitive and caring

Everyone is subject to the first, but not everyone sees or notices the second. When they do, they may mistype an entp as an F type, because they are so genuinely soft. Here are some entp heart eyes for your entertainment purposes.

I really need to find some female entps. I know plenty in real life but can’t seem to find celebrities 😂

I should also add entps can, on occasion, be pushovers because of weak Fe. Just challenge their Ti and they’ll stand up for themselves again :)

summary:
NEW PROJECT: David Tennant & Emily Watson Reunite For New Feature Film Quicksand

  

David Tennant and Emily Watson will star...
caption:
NEW PROJECT: David Tennant & Emily Watson Reunite For New Feature Film Quicksand

David Tennant and Emily Watson will star in the psychological thriller Quicksand, set to begin shooting in 2019. The pair starred together in the BBC miniseries The Politician’s Husband which aired in 2013.

Quicksand marks the feature film directorial debut of Mark Brozel (Humans, Troy: Fall Of A City), and is scripted by Steve Lewis and Tony Owen. Mark Lavender of Rough Sea Productions and Joel Scott-Halkes of Osiko Films will produce with Tannaz Anisi and Greg Schenz executive producing for 13 Films and Peter Garde, in cooperation with Indigo View.

Quicksand focuses on a British couple, Dan and Sarah, living out their dream in the Mediterranean. But their paradise comes to an abrupt end when their visiting son is murdered by a local youth. The grief stricken Dan is offered a chance at revenge by a dangerous stranger who won’t take no for an answer, but the price of revenge is one more murder.

The film will shoot on location on Crete from April next year. Sales of the project will commence at the American Film Market, from Oct. 31st in Santa Monica, California.
